The paper deals with a clustering algorithm (DBSCAN) and proposes a new approach to reduce its time complexity. This falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also uses randomized algorithms and clustering techniques, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
